business_info.name: Café 651
business_info.address: 11th B Rd, Sardarpura, Bhagat Ki Kothi, Jodhpur, Rajasthan 342003, India

reviews.content: Taste wise, the best place in Jodhpur! Loved the ambience too
The only place in Jodhpur with actually good coffee. They use a medium roast beans unlike the really dark roast used everywhere else here
This place is love. Loveee the food, in particular pasta, pizza, pancake and coffee are the must try from the menu.
